F1/home		Close/open main menu

W		Move player forward
S		Move back
A		Move left
D       Move right

Hold shift and use Arrow keys       Move camera

Enter		Decide/talk/exam/pick up
Down (arrow)	Normal attk
Right		Skill attack
Up(hold)+down	Other techs on rod

Up, then Down		Handgun
Left (tap)		Reset cam
Left (hold)     Lock On
Left(hold)+ W/S/A/D	Strafe	
E(hold)+ up/down	Action pallet/lock on menu

F2		Inventory shortcut
F3		Map shortcut
F4		Party shortcut
M		Menu item
Q		First person view

Lock on can be changed to a Toggle in the options menu.
